# Dehydrator Oven Controller — Quick Summary

## Goal
Embedded temperature control driver for a faculty dehydrator oven.

## My role
Electronics design (schematic/PCB), firmware development, and integration (plus partial 3D/mechanical integration).

## System overview
- MCU: (ESP32 / STM32 / Arduino — specify)
- Sensors: (e.g., NTC / thermocouple / DS18B20 — specify)
- Actuation: (MOSFET / SSR / TRIAC — specify)
- Control: (On/Off with hysteresis / PID — specify)

## Key features
- Temperature acquisition + filtering
- Safety logic (limits / sensor fault handling) if applicable
- Maintainable wiring + modular firmware

